Meet David Grotto, MS, RDN, LDN, FAND - one of the men I interviewed in the "Men in Nutrition" video series. See what he has to say on how he got into the field of nutrition and dietetics, what he's currently doing, why we could benefit from having more men in the profession, and finally a health tip for folks. Thanks for your help with this project Dave #nutrition #eatright #rdn #rdchat https://lnkd.in/gBfiq5mG
